      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im studying for my food science final and im a bit stuck on the browning process. can u explain the maillard reaction in detail? specifically i need to know what the temperature ranges are and what chemicals are actually interacting to make the crust turn brown. thanks",
      "source": "evaluator"
